8) [Law Seeder          ] [Ready   ] Sets up Legal Enforcement, Laws, and some related AI.
9) [Human Seeder        ] [Update  ] Adds a human race and associated data to the game
10) [Culture Seeder      ] [Update  ] Add Name Cultures, Random Names and optionally culture packs
11) [Kickstart           ] [Update  ] A collection of useful stock items, AI, tags, covers and
