Your choice: Loading package...
Package: Health Seeder
Tagline: Sets up surgeries, drugs, and medical starter content

	Installs a release-ready medical starter set for the selected tech level, including
	human surgery, a broader drug catalogue, and basic veterinary procedures for stock
	mammal bodies when those bodies are available.

Status: Ready
This package is ready to install.

Reruns reuse stock medical knowledges, procedures, phases, and drugs by stable names.

